{"tid":751923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"招人夾租/出租房間","createTime":"2018-07-22T10:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T23:47:05.000Z","uid":161115,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e305ef0d0ef92f14f9ae9b477d4853ad42a328d","tid":751923,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n因為屋企問題，無得住，急需搵地方搬。而家已經暫時住係朋友度，但唔可以打擾太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只要唔好太偏遠，盡量乾淨，同有個床位有少少空間比我擺野就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望搵到人夾<br />\n<br />\n利申:巴打，想搵長租，唔會突然退租，可以簽合約，最少一年都得，短期有人出租等我可以住住先都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩大家幫幫手<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/haydentsang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhaydentsang&d=TX7dcU1hfrmzBqCl9MW4zKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=94702255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/haydentsang</a>"},{"pid":"f3e36ef58c29c01bca718b64ffc49bb4976546b8","tid":751923,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8c80340dd4ddb247d25311daede3183f9def7c","tid":751923,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1218b265afdfad12f2a492f2a2d246f22b45fd03","tid":751923,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"做炮房ok?"},{"pid":"6a19a54dbac373d281654cd88b0aeb44d3507128","tid":751923,"uid":161115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e548a18b0cf5ff1d1fe9dfea2948f98933f2ff8","tid":751923,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018